%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.24/vllm-orchestrator-gateway.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP plaintext
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant vLLM as vLLM / LLM Runtime
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>(e.g., regex-language)

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 1: Guardrailed Chat Completion Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext<br/>Authorization header (optional)
    Note over Gateway: Loads detector config for route<br/>Injects detector specs into request<br/>Forwards Authorization + x-forwarded-* headers

    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP or HTTPS (optional mTLS)<br/>mTLS client cert + Auth header

    Orchestrator->>Detector: Run input detectors<br/>(e.g., PII detection)
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection results

    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Inference request<br/>(if input passes)
    vLLM-->>Orchestrator: Model response

    Orchestrator->>Detector: Run output detectors<br/>(e.g., content filtering)
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection results

    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: Response with detections

    alt Detections found & fallback configured
        Note over Gateway: Replace response content<br/>with fallback_message<br/>Preserve response structure
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTP Response<br/>(fallback message)
    else No detections or no fallback
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTP Response<br/>(model output)
    end

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 2: Passthrough (No Detectors)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /passthrough/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext
    Note over Gateway: No detectors configured<br/>Empty detector list

    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP or HTTPS (optional mTLS)<br/>No detector specs
    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Direct inference request
    vLLM-->>Orchestrator: Model response
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: Response (no detection)
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTP Response<br/>(model output directly)
